    • code

      CodeBlockBuilder<MethodBuilder<Result>> code(List<String> parameterNames)
      Builds code for this method or constructor.
      Parameters:
      parameterNames - names of method parameters that will be assigned to local variables. Their number must match number of types in the method descriptor. The names may differ from the ones given in parameter() method and may be empty strings if the corresponding local is to remain anonymous.
